      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a 8,000 RPM redline via individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains factory-spec with no subframe fatigue, riding on staggered Style 67 forged alloys. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current; the paint meter readings are consistent across all panels. A true driver\u2019s car preserved in its most visceral form.",
